---
title: Jerk Chicken Tostadas with Sweetcorn and Tomatoes
description: Create a slice of Caribbean heaven in your kitchen with our delicious Jamaican Jerk Chicken tostadas. Jerk chicken, a typical Jamaican street food, is traditionally cooked for hours over fires made from the aromatic wood of allspice trees. And it’s allspice together with hot peppers, ginger and thyme that give Jerk it’s distinctive flavour. Crispy tostadas are topped with zingy chicken and sweetcorn, and served with a dollop of coconut crema and a fresh zingy salad. Feel the sunshine...
